hong kong. direct trains run from hong kong's hung hom direct to guangzhou east station. immigration is done at the respective station rather that at the border. some trains also stop at other guangdong stations. the hong kong mtr runs from the city to 2 points on the shenzhen border. the main border crossing is at lo wu/luo hu, which is next to shenzhen's main station. vietnam - from nanning in guangxi province into vietnam via the friendship pass. services from kunming have been suspended since 2002. north korea - four weekly connections between the north korean capital pyongyang and 